flowchart TD
  A[sensor_data from PYNQ] --> P[protocol.py<br/>decode and validate]
  P --> C[classifier_adapter.py<br/>sleep_result]
  P --> SVC[service.py]
  C --> SVC
  SVC --> POL[comfort_policy.py<br/>control_command]
  SVC --> STATE[state_store.py<br/>latest state and histories]
  SVC --> STOR[storage.py<br/>four JSONL streams]
  POL --> OUT[send sleep_result + control_command]
  OUT --> PYNQ[PYNQ applies or skips command]
  PYNQ --> STATUS[control_status]
  STATUS --> P
  P --> SVC

